As I see it Nintendo has abandoned their traditional competition with Sony and Microsoft in favor of appealing to a different set of gamers. It's plausible that a Valve console could compete alongside Sony and Microsoft in the "hardcore" market while Nintendo keeps on pursuing the more casual crowd.
